metadata.name: Sleepwalkers #1
metadata.description:
The third collection of work from Modern Vintage Photos continues to explore the gifts the universe has given us. "Sleepwalkers" delves into the world of dreams, creativity and the subconscious.

Science has learned many things about humans, but one area that still holds great mystery is the subconscious. How and why do we dream? Where do creativity and inspiration come from?

Artists do our best to feed it and give it space to gestate. That intangible place between conscious and unconscious, between states of wake and sleep is where we like to reside. 

Modern Vintage Photos believes this magical place is where we can find healing and solace. attempt to get in touch with the soul.

"Sleepwalkers" is an attempt to explore those experiences and create visual connections that bring the viewer into the spaces we discover.
